Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.31,0:00:19.88,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have proof of your devilish plot, Dio!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.90,0:00:25.70,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's caught me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.60,0:00:28.22,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't run.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.63,0:00:32.17,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I came back here to fight JoJo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.11,0:00:51.57,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Two stars fallen from the heavens
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.36,0:00:58.74,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Swallowed by waters swirling\Nlight and dark
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.98,0:01:03.92,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Their ripples move outward,\Npulled toward each other
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.84,0:01:15.44,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The sun will guide the man\Nwho walks the path of honor
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.44,0:01:21.14,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And for the man who follows\Nhis ambition...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.56,0:01:23.35,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,...a sacrifice awaits
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.73,0:01:33.45,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With pounding heart\Nand burning will
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.45,0:01:36.96,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With thundering fists
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.96,0:01:40.58,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And overflowing bravery
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.58,0:01:46.58,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He steps forward, free of doubt
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.13,0:01:50.48,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A fate determined by his blood
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.26,0:01:54.72,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.01,0:02:11.06,Type,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chapter 3: Time With Dio
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.14,0:02:11.06,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,ADJUSTMENT	I found the antidote.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.22,0:02:13.86,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dad just took it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.01,0:02:18.06,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dio, I'm heartbroken.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.39,0:02:22.87,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We were raised as brothers and now\NI have to turn you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:24.05,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.20,0:02:29.22,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You might not believe that,\Nbut I mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.47,0:02:34.09,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That compassion is very like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.70,0:02:40.90,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo, this is selfish,\Nbut I have a final favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:46.35,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please, give me time.\NTime to turn myself in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.97,0:02:48.16,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.16,0:02:52.50,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I expected him to fight\Nlike a cornered animal!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.72,0:02:58.20,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo, how did you make it\Nout of that slum alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.20,0:03:02.82,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to distract him,\Nthen with one quick stab...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.82,0:03:05.92,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I regret my life until now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.92,0:03:09.83,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Being poor when I was a child\Nmade me greedy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.47,0:03:12.22,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What I did was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.22,0:03:16.09,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to poison and rob\Nthe man who raised me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.78,0:03:19.76,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I came back to turn myself in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:23.82,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I wanted to run,\NI could have gone anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.82,0:03:25.30,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:28.01,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make amends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.01,0:03:28.89,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dio --
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.89,0:03:33.40,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Careful, Jonathan.\NDon't trust a word that snake says.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.70,0:03:39.11,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I, you ask?\NAllow me to introduce myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:42.43,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Robert E. O. Speedwagon,\Nthe meddler.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.43,0:03:46.74,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried about Jonathan,\Nso I came back with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.40,0:03:51.75,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Since I like you, Jonathan,\Nlet me tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.07,0:03:56.78,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was raised in squalor,\Nand I've seen a lot of lowlifes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.78,0:04:01.14,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My nose knows the difference\Nbetween good and bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:06.69,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And this guy stinks worse\Nthan a pile of puke!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.69,0:04:10.23,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've never met a man\Nas wicked as him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.74,0:04:14.23,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wicked because of circumstance? No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.65,0:04:17.20,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This man was born bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:23.45,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This face is familiar to you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.15,0:04:28.95,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This man has testified\Nthat he sold you the poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.40,0:04:32.20,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:35.28,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is truly a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.74,0:04:41.67,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I put the same love and hope into you\Nas I did my own son.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:45.95,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, you need to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.95,0:04:49.14,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right, I'll go to bed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.75,0:04:52.89,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to see my son arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.24,0:04:55.24,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo, do what you must.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.49,0:04:56.40,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.36,0:04:59.52,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.52,0:05:02.45,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They won't catch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.20,0:05:06.40,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That face and three moles on his ear...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:09.91,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He was born with the devil's own luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:16.92,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo, I want you to be the one\Nto handcuff me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.13,0:05:18.72,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,For our years together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.40,0:05:20.40,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.99,0:05:23.92,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, Jonathan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.46,0:05:28.94,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo, being human means having limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.07,0:05:32.45,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've learned something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.32,0:05:36.20,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The more carefully you scheme,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:39.69,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nthe more unexpected events come along.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.34,0:05:42.45,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you are human...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.72,0:05:44.78,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What? What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.19,0:05:48.76,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm throwing away my humanity, JoJo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.65,0:05:52.87,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm moving beyond humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:54.86,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.86,0:05:55.89,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.89,0:05:57.12,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot him now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:05:59.63,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use your blood, JoJo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.05,0:06:07.07,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.67,0:06:10.47,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.68,0:06:21.44,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:38.53,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.34,0:06:40.98,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.52,0:06:46.30,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I should have dodged that knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.94,0:06:49.55,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I let the mask distract me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.40,0:06:52.10,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You sacrificed yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:56.56,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.27,0:07:00.56,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was your mother's.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:03.06,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.10,0:07:06.15,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That wound is fatal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:08.52,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How could I let that happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.29,0:07:12.46,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Joestar... I told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.35,0:07:19.35,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault. If only I\Nhad banished Dio's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.35,0:07:21.29,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dio's father?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:25.66,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When I first joined the force,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.66,0:07:30.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,there was a man who tried to pawn that ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.12,0:07:34.48,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was Dio's father, Dario Brando.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:38.40,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's definitely my ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:42.30,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We had a pair made when\Nwe were engaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.93,0:07:47.15,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A burglar named Dario Brando\Nwas trying to pawn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.27,0:07:49.44,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Brando!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:54.65,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Joestar thought he owed\Na life debt to Dario Brando.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.52,0:08:03.15,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But Brando was just a thief rooting\Naround for gold at the accident site!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.44,0:08:05.53,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.10,0:08:12.81,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did he happen to tell you that\NI gave him the ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.81,0:08:16.47,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He did. What a flimsy lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.47,0:08:18.11,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.48,0:08:20.77,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I did give it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.77,0:08:22.81,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:25.15,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He is innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:27.65,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.65,0:08:29.82,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you let him go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:35.02,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I were born in his circumstances,\NI may have done the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.43,0:08:41.29,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sell this and buy something\Nfor your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:46.48,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then forsake criminality\Nand walk an honest path.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:53.55,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Joestar knew the whole truth\Nbefore he adopted Dio.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.81,0:08:57.55,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, Dad.\NThe doctors will save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.11,0:09:01.79,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo, please don't hate Dio.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.30,0:09:04.02,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I am responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.12,0:09:09.00,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was hard on you because\Nyou are my real son.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.00,0:09:13.94,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But in Dio's eyes, that may have been\Nunfair to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.56,0:09:17.94,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That could have driven him\Nto do what he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:23.44,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please bury him next to his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:25.87,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.45,0:09:33.46,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo, it's not so bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:37.83,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,...to die in the arms\Nof your own son.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.03,0:09:45.79,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Joestar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.04,0:09:50.39,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What a tragedy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:54.78,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now his kindness is gone from the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.00,0:09:55.78,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:10:01.79,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Joestar passed his noble spirit\Nalong to Jonathan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.32,0:10:07.79,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It has become his iron will, his pride\Nand it will create his future!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.20,0:10:13.08,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Normally I hate spoiled crybabies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.95,0:10:15.79,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But they are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:21.24,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They live life with no regrets.\NThey're giants!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:26.55,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,T-The body!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.05,0:10:29.99,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dio Brando's body is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.12,0:10:35.07,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You, cop! Get away from the window!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.79,0:10:57.45,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,H-His head...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.77,0:11:01.80,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:05.06,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How?! We filled him with bullets!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:07.56,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out! I'm sure he has a weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.91,0:11:12.31,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.04,0:11:16.25,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's coming this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.25,0:11:18.82,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you waiting for?! Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.91,0:11:20.95,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dio, stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.84,0:11:27.29,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dio!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.11,0:11:32.77,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and\Npull the trigger, Jonathan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.15,0:12:05.53,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's not dead, even after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.53,0:12:10.99,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.\NI can't understand what's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.37,0:12:13.00,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How could this be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.78,0:12:14.50,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.82,0:12:22.76,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This marvelous power comes from\Nthe mask, and your father's blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.07,0:12:33.36,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's sucking out that man's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.15,0:12:37.86,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dio, just what have you become?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.15,0:12:52.99,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm so confused...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:57.54,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The knife... Dad's death...\NBlood... Dio... The mask...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:13:01.55,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My notes... The brain...\NUnknown abilities... Unknown strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:04.77,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dio, you aren't human anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.28,0:13:13.28,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.88,0:13:24.03,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! You don't stand a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.15,0:13:30.28,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen the like!\NAnything that powerful is a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.90,0:13:31.78,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.74,0:13:34.90,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.18,0:13:38.33,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But Dio, I can't let you live like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.53,0:13:40.96,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault. I'll finish it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:43.59,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan, stop! You'll just be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:51.03,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The brain! The mask unlocks\Nthe brain's hidden potential!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.44,0:13:53.85,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So in order to beat Dio...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.33,0:14:04.42,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The bodies!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.42,0:14:06.44,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Warm blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.44,0:14:08.61,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want to lick it all up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:19.78,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mind if\NI suck your blood, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.84,0:14:34.37,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is hard. He was my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.77,0:14:38.52,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, please lend me your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:45.60,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have to be strong.\NDio is no longer human.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.60,0:14:46.74,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.52,0:14:48.15,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.44,0:14:55.16,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let Dio kill another person!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.85,0:15:00.42,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,H-He caught it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.19,0:15:04.02,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even after it went through his hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.27,0:15:09.23,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, the hole in his head\Nhas already healed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.44,0:15:12.35,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's completely immortal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.94,0:15:18.73,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're weak! So weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:28.47,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.47,0:15:34.10,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have to play with you a bit more\Nto test out my new powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.98,0:15:39.19,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even I don't know how far they go yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:43.75,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.65,0:16:05.19,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I just tell you?\NHuman schemes have their limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.85,0:16:08.42,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cease your useless struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.42,0:16:12.56,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cowering behind the curtains, are we?\NCome on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.03,0:16:19.29,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a scheme. It's courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.85,0:16:30.61,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's regenerating while he burns!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.96,0:16:33.51,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the source of his immortality?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.15,0:16:36.10,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This fire isn't enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.02,0:16:45.77,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:50.57,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of here, Speedwagon!\NThis doesn't concern you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.06,0:17:12.26,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You can't go up!\NThe fire is spreading!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.69,0:17:20.43,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan, what are you planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.35,0:17:27.19,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come on up, Dio!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.69,0:17:40.33,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dio, I won't let you go\Nbeyond these walls!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.59,0:17:42.16,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.36,0:17:52.95,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is he using himself as bait\Nto protect his friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.77,0:17:54.98,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.51,0:18:02.94,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just use your blood\Nto heal these burns.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.98,0:18:12.69,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fleeing up here is useless!\NFalling from this high won't hurt me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.67,0:18:17.72,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Instead, now the fire has cornered you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.43,0:18:22.19,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.48,0:18:29.52,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, I'll miss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.97,0:18:33.88,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please go to heaven\Nalong with those flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.93,0:18:38.02,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And then, help me accomplish my goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:41.67,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Give your strength to the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.86,0:18:47.27,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is Jonathan doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.05,0:18:52.06,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No! He couldn't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.26,0:18:55.94,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! You mustn't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.15,0:19:00.43,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,H-Here he comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.88,0:19:11.63,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Utterly pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.36,0:19:16.13,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly, JoJo's youth\Nflashed through his mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.78,0:19:29.27,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My youth...\NMy time with Dio...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.80,0:19:34.02,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm going to settle the score\Nfor all that time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.85,0:19:39.53,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's trying to make the fire\Nburn as hot as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:45.03,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If the fire burns Dio faster than\Nhe can regenerate, he'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.86,0:19:51.04,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So Jonathan waited for the flames\Nto spread before going to the roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.01,0:19:53.67,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.77,0:20:00.34,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,H-How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.05,0:20:04.87,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The mansion my ancestors lived in\Nis burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.30,0:20:11.42,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dad is dead, I have nothing left.\NNothing but my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.68,0:20:16.94,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let myself burn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:20.63,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll end your ambition\Nin exchange for my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.77,0:20:25.03,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, JoJo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.23,0:20:30.37,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,For a second there I admired your guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.95,0:20:35.18,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now cry tears of joy\Nsince you can die with your dad, fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.84,0:20:42.37,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm beyond human! Invincible! Immortal!\NI will rule this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.37,0:20:45.14,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo, you gave me this power!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.03,0:20:58.65,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't reach!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.45,0:21:06.57,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dio, I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.70,0:21:08.33,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?! How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.31,0:21:12.00,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.00,0:21:15.00,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your fate is sealed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.29,0:21:22.92,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here! This is the knife\Nyou killed my father with!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.26,0:21:35.66,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've crushed his arms to dust and he's
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.66,0:21:39.13,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,\Non fire, but he just won't let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.13,0:21:43.36,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Very well!\NLet's go into the inferno together!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.52,0:21:46.01,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But you'll die alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.01,0:21:50.87,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find a way to escape,\Nno matter how hot it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.32,0:21:56.56,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! Lend me your aid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.56,0:21:58.88,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A scream! A desperate cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.44,0:22:02.57,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Whether at an urge from beyond or
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.57,0:22:07.34,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nan instinct to use his burning home...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.02,0:22:08.84,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo kicked!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.10,0:22:11.08,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And across from that spot...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.18,0:22:13.52,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What the --
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.30,0:22:19.35,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,...was a statue of the Joestar \Nfamily's guardian angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.51,0:22:26.12,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How could a worm like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.38,0:22:29.32,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I completely forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.32,0:22:34.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The more you beat him, the tougher he gets!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.42,0:22:38.55,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.55,0:22:44.03,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This wasn't what my life\Nwas supposed to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.34,0:22:52.51,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.85,0:22:57.02,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.62,0:22:58.78,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.65,0:23:01.02,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.69,0:23:03.16,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.06,0:23:08.52,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He won!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.91,0:24:52.09,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.65,0:25:10.65,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.19,0:25:12.79,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Courage is knowing fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.79,0:25:15.42,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's worse than Dio!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.42,0:25:17.35,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wriggle in despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.35,0:25:18.91,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who do I look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.91,0:25:21.66,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please, teach me how to use Hamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.66,0:25:23.89,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chapter 4: Overdrive
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.89,0:25:25.89,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,
